com.thinkaurelius.titan.core

Interface TitanGraphQuery<Q extends TitanGraphQuery<Q>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphCentricQueryBuilder

    public interface TitanGraphQuery<Q extends TitanGraphQuery<Q>>
    Constructs a query against a mixed index to retrieve all elements (either vertices or edges) that match all conditions.

    Finding matching elements efficiently using this query mechanism requires that appropriate index structures have been defined for the keys. See TitanManagement for more information on how to define index structures in Titan.

    Since:
    0.3.0
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
